sfDoctrineGraphvizPlugin
========================

Provides you with a task that output database MCD and MLD doctrine schema
using the graphviz tool.

Installation
============

Install the plugin via the subversion repository:

    $ svn co http://svn.symfony-project.com/plugins/sfDoctrineGraphvizPlugin plugins/sfDoctrineGraphvizPlugin

from the project root directory or by using the command:

    $ ./symfony plugin:install sfDoctrineGraphvizPlugin

Usage
=====

Simply type the following command:

    $ ./symfony doctrine:graphviz

Files are created in the directory _doc/graph/doctrine_. There are 4 files created:

*   **mcd.schema.dot** : source of *"Modèle conceptuel des données"*
*   **mcd.schema.png** : image of *"Modèle conceptuel des données"*
*   **mld.schema.dot** : source of *"Modèle logique des données"*
*   **mld.schema.png** : image of *"Modèle logique des données"*

Notes
=====

You must have [GraphViz](http://www.graphviz.org/Documentation.php) installed
on your system.
